# Sumner Borough Land Vesting Act 1929Local Act1929 No 19

Date of assent7 November 1929

## Contents

[Title][0]

[1][1] [Short Title][1]

[2][2] [Deemed a special Act][2]

[3][3] [Vesting land in Corporation][3]

